{"tid":1265140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【未send嘅公開信】刪除TVB 83洗腦台行動已開始，促請袁志偉一個月內辭職！","createTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T05:06:47.000Z","uid":267969,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2440198d8689f77a162e53dd93f7fbdad0c8cdf4","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我將會send呢封信俾TVB<br />\n點解仲未send？<br />\n因為下面紅色嘅統計數字需要大家參與！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果你將會或實際已參與「刪除83洗腦新聞台行動」，請於#2俾正評</span><br />\n記得，我係計#2正評</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n陳國強博士、李寶安先生：<br />\n<br />\n修訂「逃犯條例」在社會上引起很大反響，引發一連串遊行、集會及示威，不少傳媒謹守崗位作出公正持平的報導，然而　貴台新聞報導偏頗，引來大量市民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n近日，網民自發參與「刪除家中83洗腦新聞台行動」，本人透過討論區作簡單統計，截至2019年7月3日中午，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">參與人數達XXXX人 (link:___)</span></strong>，本人將會傳送此信件副本予廣告商及各大傳媒作為參考。<br />\n<br />\n冰封一尺，非一日之寒，市民對　貴台之不滿由袁志偉執掌新聞部開始，只有袁志偉辭職才能平息民怨，挽救收視。<br />\n<br />\n本人現代表<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>XXXX</strong></span>市民，促請　貴台於一星期內回應 (2019年7月10日)，以及袁志偉於一個月內辭職 (2019年8月3日)。基於　貴台往績，對市民意見一直置若罔聞，本人對　貴台回應不存期望，市民已經或將會自發參與以下升級行動：<br />\n1. 罷買廣告商品<br />\n2. 在餐廳及社區內自發轉台（貴台頻道覆蓋率將進一步下降）<br />\n3. 刪除81台<br />\n<br />\n　祝<br />\n懸崖勒馬<br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民上"},{"pid":"42d72d893d50e4cbc16251f7a26d541e154ad314","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你將會或實際已參與「刪除83洗腦新聞台行動」，請在<span style=\"color: orange;\">此回覆</span>給予正評！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e2dfb980b83e07d7496b157e08d8fd868f4a6a07","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"隔離post，HKismyhome絲打已有廣告商名單，遲下有時間會砌Google form俾大家幫手入FB, email，請用追故模式追蹤我嘅update，請踴躍參與。"},{"pid":"e15d896fc21bb9da3b0969ad1bdf02dc5b44a2bb","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"d0645556dc7d5b4b331cb8bc0ea622cfeeca9cd7","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"作為社區轉台師及孝順仔，已經幫父母刪台，較定時去睇99台新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpjr6D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqpjr6D.jpg&h=9d8a8109&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSwayMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSwayMF.jpg&h=3333e2ff&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8d2QyMG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8d2QyMG.jpg&h=4480751b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊SAMSUNG機只可以定時一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c589b00c18f23a7b474edd95084a15996f9cdb13","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649e88c34c296f1fb7f2780766038da8c166e743","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"買遙控轉台post有人理，認真post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaf6cdcd6dd57f9322972e8d9059a50f1d2ecb8","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推推"},{"pid":"34bfb72b7bc27478914062e43757b40d2719441b","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c73d7c431dba180915e724335d8bad928dec510","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab3fd06f281e16832e07efaf6c5167f3475612c","tid":1265140,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike"